I am working to achieve the function for user to generate their trip plan into a pdf that they can carry around with them. [react-pdf](https://react-pdf.org/) is a very powerful tool for me to achieve this goal.

# Prevent SSR in Next.js 
As the web rendering functions of react-pdf only work on client side, the first problem I faced was to prevent server side rendering. I wrote [another blog](https://niuniuanran.github.io/2020/05/07/Prevent-Next-js-Server-Side-Rendering/) on this issue.

# Code for a nice pdf
